editSplit(25.10)                                              editSplit(25.10)

Name
       editSplit - Splits selected special wires at connection points with or-
       thogonal wires

Syntax
       editSplit [-help]

       Splits  selected  special  wires  at  connection points with orthogonal
       wires. This command can also be used to split selected bus guides.

       Note: Use the editSelect command to select the wires. Use  the  select-
       BusGuide command to select bus guides or bus guide segments

Parameters
       -help  Prints  the  usage of the command. For a detailed description of
              the command, use the man command:

              man editSplit

